node.text: The newly-enhanced Jungle Cruise attraction officially opens to explorers today and the mischievous wildlife are ready at Disneyland park! Watch as we highlight a few familiar favorites along with the new fun you can find on this sometimes perilous, always hilarious river adventure! For more, visit the Disney Parks Blog (link in bio).

node.title: Charting New Adventures on the World-Famous Jungle Cruise

RECIPE ALERT: Celebrate #DOLEWhipDay at home with this Frozen Pineapple Treat inspired by DOLE Whip and our watch list of tropical island favorites on #DisneyPlus! Find the recipe below, full watch list and a printable version of the recipe on the Disney Parks Blog now (link in bio).

Frozen Pineapple Treat Inspired by DOLE Whip
(Serves 4)

Ingredients: 
🍍1/2-3/4 cup pineapple juice, divided 
🍍2 cups frozen pineapple chunks 
🍍1 cup dairy-free vanilla ice cream 

Directions:
🍦1. Place 1/2 cup pineapple juice, frozen pineapple, and dairy-free vanilla ice cream in a blender and blend until smooth - do not over blend. If the mixture is too thick to blend, add 2 tablespoons of pineapple juice at a time. 
🍦2. Scoop into bowls and serve immediately.

node.text: #DOLEWhipDay is today and we're honoring THE sweet treat of Disney Parks! 🍍 Check out our Disney Parks Foodie Guide to All Your DOLE Whip Dreams on the Disney Parks Blog (link in bio) for a listing of the current current offerings to celebrate properly!

The search is on for Disney Magic Makers! Do you know someone who makes magic by bringing comfort, support and joy to those around them?
